def maximize_character_rating(n, k, skills):
    m = [0] / 10
    r = 0
    for a in skills:
        m[a % 10] += 1
        r += a // 10
    for i in range(1, 10):
        x = min(k // i, m[10 - i])
        k -= x * i
        r += x
    max_rating = min(r + k // 10, 10 * n)
    return max_rating
